WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'PentA' is a game in which you place 12 different shapes in such
a way that all the shapes fit in a rectangular pattern shown in
the center of the game area. Try to complete the game with the
least amount of moves.

  There are 4 different board sizes to choose from: a 3 x 20
board, a 4 x 15 board, a 5 x 12 board and a 6 x 10 board.

  Have fun!

FEATURES
